Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太難吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像泔水一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像以平靜的心情在瀑布修行的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱片點唱機砸過來時的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱片點唱機？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.02,0:24:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非 非常抱歉 繪裏奈大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.40,0:24:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 笑都笑不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都笑不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下話 食戟之靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二道菜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神之舌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.84,0:24:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,God Tongue
